<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id059031da-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s1756"><num value="1756">§ 1756.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Treasury may prescribe such regulations as may be necessary or appropriate to carry out the provisions of this chapter (other than section 1751 thereof).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id059031db-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/14/s7">Pub. L. 86–14, § 7</ref>, <date date="1959-04-22">Apr. 22, 1959</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/73/19">73 Stat. 19</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
